                <h4>Online Portal Enhancements</h4>
                <p style="color: gray; font-size: 0.9rem;">January 5, 2024</p>
                <p>
                    The NBT registration portal has been upgraded with improved mobile responsiveness 
                    and faster loading times. Candidates can now also update their test venue preferences 
                    up to 48 hours before their scheduled test.
                </p>
            </div>

            <FluentDivider />

            <div>
                <h4>Results Retrieval System Update</h4>
                <p style="color: gray; font-size: 0.9rem;">December 1, 2023</p>
                <p>
                    The results retrieval system has been updated to provide more detailed performance 
                    feedback and downloadable result certificates for candidates.
                </p>
            </div>
        </FluentStack>
    </FluentCard>

    <!-- Upcoming Events -->
    <FluentCard>
        <FluentStack Orientation="Orientation.Vertical" VerticalGap="16">
            <h2>ðŸŽ“ Upcoming Events</h2>
