            <div>
                <h4>Educator Workshops - March 2024</h4>
                <p>
                    CETAP will be conducting NBT information workshops for educators across South Africa. 
                    These workshops will cover test content, student preparation strategies, and understanding 
                    NBT results. Registration details will be announced in February.
                </p>
            </div>

            <FluentDivider />

            <div>
                <h4>Annual Research Conference - June 2024</h4>
                <p>
                    The Annual NBT Research Conference will be held in Cape Town in June 2024. The conference 
                    will bring together researchers, practitioners, and policymakers to discuss academic 
                    preparedness and student success in higher education.
                </p>
            </div>
        </FluentStack>
    </FluentCard>

    <!-- Archive -->
    <FluentCard Style="background: #f3f2f1;">
        <FluentStack Orientation="Orientation.Vertical" VerticalGap="12">
            <h3>ðŸ“š News Archive</h3>
